                    },
                    "body": "patch for ZF-12086: adding custom_translations option to Zend_Service_ReCaptcha.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wenz",
                        "name": "wenz",
                        "displayName": "Christian Wenz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-03-03T21:52:26.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-03-03T21:52:26.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/49900",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=szogun1987",
                        "name": "szogun1987",
                        "displayName": "Wojciech Gomo\u0142a",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I think that I found better solution. Zend_Captcha_ReCaptcha should have \"IsCustomTranslated\" property. If user call \"setCustomTranslated(true)\" rendering should use translation engine to translate all 9 phrases and set \"custom_translation\" to right value.h",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=szogun1987",
                        "name": "szogun1987",
                        "displayName": "Wojciech Gomo\u0142a",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-03-04T06:19:58.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-03-04T06:19:58.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/49904",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wenz",
                        "name": "wenz",
                        "displayName": "Christian Wenz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I believe the proposed patch offers a more flexible solution; relying on a translating engine would lead to nondeterministic results if the translation engine is updated, what is probably undesirable.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wenz",
                        "name": "wenz",
                        "displayName": "Christian Wenz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-03-04T17:26:42.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-03-04T17:26:42.000+0000"
                },
                {
